  "3092580": {
    "name": "许愿岛 Hope Isle",
    "steam_appid": 3092580,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092580/extras/3e68adfff0f77dca69a6c74fe3031492.avif?t=1753174689\" width=614 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在某一天，忧伤之海中长出了一颗高耸入云的希望之树，在这棵树底部逐渐形成了一座小岛，也就是我们的许愿岛。您可以在游戏中写下心愿，岛上的祈灵们会为了愿望成真而虔诚祈祷。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“有的愿望只适合藏在心里”，如果您不希望让你写下的愿望总是被别人看到，也可以把愿望切换为<strong>加密符文</strong>。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092580/extras/e8217d032c3ce90a9322db2aeba0da9e.webp?t=1753174689\" width=358 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现这座岛的人就是许愿岛的主人，<strong>也就是您</strong>。您可以召唤更多的祈灵，亦可以扩张和建设这座岛，为小岛添加更多的生活功能，比如商店、钓鱼、耕种等等。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于这座岛存在于另外一个位面，岛主只能通过一束光来和岛上的诸多事物进行交互，祈灵们也要通过这束光来感受岛主的关注和呵护。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092580/extras/cca72d3b3bb606783161812773593868.avif?t=1753174689\" width=614 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092580/extras/8c300c74eac82e161b49b041488f60bd.webp?t=1753174689\" width=519 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >岛屿附近的海域里物产丰富，岛上肥沃的土壤也适宜种植多种作物，通过钓鱼、耕种和商店获取这些物资。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着流程推进，您还将解锁烹饪和制作功能，利用物资制作祈灵们喜欢的食物和玩具，丰富他们的生活。他们的快乐和满足将会是岛主的宝贵财富，也会更加卖力为您的愿望祈祷。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092580/extras/b1cd86fc91f38d4e8433cf93f207b279.avif?t=1753174689\" width=615 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092580/extras/5a1ea744e87e290f01845fc40ad5d7ad.webp?t=1753174689\" width=396 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >祈祷是祈灵们与生俱来的工作，在工作之余祈灵们也会享受他们的个人时光，在岛主设计的小世界里任意休憩或玩耍。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于性格各异，在岛上偶然相遇的他们可以成为挚友亦可能关系紧张。您需要在闲暇之余照看岛民的心情，适当的投下光柱，引导这些小生灵解决他们的烦恼，或者和它们分享当下的快乐与满足！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092580/extras/03ec6c42f9f27a091720991bf63c8664.avif?t=1753174689\" width=615 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092580/extras/cdbe5044865fea25685457ef48ae6647.webp?t=1753174689\" width=337 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >祈灵们会日复一日地爬上树冠继续祈祷，岛主们也要在自己的世界继续自己的生活。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092580/extras/414ac348565bb3e8580484a54a9607be.avif?t=1753174689\" width=614 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了在岛上和祈灵们相会，您也可以把它们<i>召唤到电脑桌面</i>上，让它们在游戏之外陪你度过忙碌的时光。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092580/extras/fcadb23c28822b97473463b39bcd672b.poster.avif?t=1753174689\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092580/extras/fcadb23c28822b97473463b39bcd672b.webm?t=1753174689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092580/extras/fcadb23c28822b97473463b39bcd672b.mp4?t=1753174689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
